Package: libcutiescreenlock
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         libpam-runtime
Description: Screen-lock authentication engine for Cutie Shell.
 PAM-backed password auth plus locally hashed PIN/pattern secrets,
 exposed over D-Bus as org.cutie_shell.ScreenLock.

Package: qml6-module-cutiescreenlock
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         libcutiescreenlock (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Cutie.ScreenLock QML module.
 Provides the CutieScreenLock QML type (a D-Bus client for
 org.cutie_shell.ScreenLock) plus the PinPad and PatternLock QML
 components, for use by cutie-panel's lockscreen and cutie-settings.

Package: libcutiescreenlock-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         libcutiescreenlock (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Development files for libcutiescreenlock.
 Headers needed to link CutieScreenLockAuthority directly (cutie-panel
 only - everything else should use the Cutie.ScreenLock QML module
 instead).
